dag.query:
WITH preprocessing_steps AS
(
    SELECT
    CustomerId AS c_i_211,
    Exited AS c_i_212,
    Age AS c_i_213,
    Balance AS c_i_214,
    CreditScore AS c_i_215,
    EstimatedSalary AS c_i_216,
    Tenure AS c_i_217,
    Gender AS c_i_218,
    Geography AS c_i_219,
    NumOfProducts AS c_i_220,
    HasCrCard AS c_i_221,
    IsActiveMember AS c_i_222,
    COALESCE( c_i_213 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_223,
    CASE WHEN c_i_214 < 1 THEN 1 ELSE c_i_214 END AS c_i_236,
    COALESCE( c_i_215 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_224,
    CASE WHEN c_i_216 < 1 THEN 1 ELSE c_i_216 END AS c_i_237,
    COALESCE( c_i_217 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_225,
    CASE c_i_218 WHEN 'Female' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END  AS c_i_234,
    COALESCE( c_i_219 , 'France' ) AS c_i_229,
    COALESCE( c_i_220 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_226,
    COALESCE( c_i_221 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_227,
    COALESCE( c_i_222 , 0.0 ) AS c_i_228,
    CASE WHEN c_i_223 > 100 THEN 100 ELSE CASE WHEN c_i_223 < 10 THEN 10 ELSE c_i_223 END END AS c_i_235,
     LN(( c_i_236 ))  AS c_i_238,
    CAST( (c_i_224) AS FLOAT ) AS c_i_240,
     LN(( c_i_237 ))  AS c_i_239,
    CAST( (c_i_225) AS FLOAT ) AS c_i_241,
    CASE c_i_229 WHEN 'France' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END  AS c_i_230,
    CASE c_i_229 WHEN 'Spain' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END  AS c_i_231,
    CASE c_i_229 WHEN 'Germany' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END  AS c_i_232,
    CASE WHEN (c_i_229) IS NOT IN ('France', 'Spain', 'Germany') THEN 1 ELSE 0 END  AS c_i_233,
    CAST( (c_i_226) AS FLOAT ) AS c_i_242
    FROM
        ${table_view} t
)

SELECT
    c_i_211 AS CustomerId,
    c_i_212 AS Exited,
    c_i_235 AS Age,
    c_i_238 AS Balance,
    c_i_240 AS CreditScore,
    c_i_239 AS EstimatedSalary,
    c_i_241 AS Tenure,
    c_i_234 AS Gender,
    c_i_230 AS Geography__OHE_1_France,
    c_i_231 AS Geography__OHE_2_Spain,
    c_i_232 AS Geography__OHE_3_Germany,
    c_i_233 AS Geography__OHE_0_otherwise,
    c_i_242 AS NumOfProducts,
    c_i_227 AS HasCrCard,
    c_i_228 AS IsActiveMember
FROM
preprocessing_steps t
